,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淘咁麻煩 IG有啲ac專租呢啲晚裝</blockquote><br />\n都唔知衛生唔衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 租呢d好多都唔係成日洗 整污糟又賠錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084dbb1a3c48697e7e7779e50501e84497c41f8d","tid":231503,"uid":106706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>155矮妹著咩裙好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好網店 想係鋪頭買<br />\n有無好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔可以著長裙<br />\n著高腰cutting既可以望落腳長d</blockquote><br />\n我都係155  都話butter n bread 佢個cutting令 我當年著都好多人話好睇 唔好選低胸 長裙 中短就好 斯打你小腿粗唔粗 如果幼就露 粗就建議你可能要中長啦 grad 當然要曬優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e850dddf2dd24528e747d3a30baed7661d6b0c5b","tid":231503,"uid":106706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>紙片人表示好難買到裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知去邊度買好</blockquote><br />\n唔好著低胸<br />\n著背心cutting呢類大路款<br />\n著吊帶款都唔錯<br />\n你生得高既話著高跟鞋show下腳都已經好靚<br />\n最緊要識突顯自己既優點<br />\n我個條其實都係商場逐間行逐間睇先搵到<br />\n搵日得閒同個朋友去行個圈交換下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n斯打真係同我同路人 想法一致 最重要唔好濃妝 咪嚇死人 唔識化妝就自己練習下 淡妝都好過濃 紙片人就買d蕾絲裙好d 瘦人顯得有氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed880b41c73dba4bb184bdad83cd5a3d8ca2a6f","tid":231503,"uid":111264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:20:39.000Z","msg":"吓 要着衫架咩"},{"pid":"41f4d499c1f58f2e50209f5daa6369a729ec06eb","tid":231503,"uid":106706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有我唔算好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會加件披肩遮一遮好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔係著低胸裙唔洗介意啦<br />\n加件薄外套已經ok<br />\n披肩由其是有毛毛個d我愈望愈覺得似結婚去做姊妹團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前grad都係 我同我fd個個都白色裙 真係一齊影好似結婚甘 不過裙都要 襯埋個頭  所以又要考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9d7056eeadeead4dc710e2225c96c6bc456eff","tid":231503,"uid":114752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:37:59.000Z","msg":"淘唔緊要 但樓主點解要揀啲咁國產味極濃嘅？"},{"pid":"fdf4980b3ab12971565440dececd3480e5d2a3fe","tid":231503,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:43:11.000Z","msg":"當年著校服去"},{"pid":"ca546d455b9de5730ffac365db5e5d9102e1cd33","tid":231503,"uid":59314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>紙片人表示好難買到裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知去邊度買好</blockquote><br />\n唔好著低胸<br />\n著背心cutting呢類大路款<br />\n著吊帶款都唔錯<br />\n你生得高既話著高跟鞋show下腳都已經好靚<br />\n最緊要識突顯自己既優點<br />\n我個條其實都係商場逐間行逐間睇先搵到<br />\n搵日得閒同個朋友去行個圈交換下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n斯打真係同我同路人 想法一致 最重要唔好濃妝 咪嚇死人 唔識化妝就自己練習下 淡妝都好過濃 紙片人就買d蕾絲裙好d 瘦人顯得有氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n濃妝真係大忌<br />\n我個陣有個好pure既同學化濃妝搞到好似老左5年咁<br />\n但係佢著既裙係好小妹妹feel既白色裙搞到成個look勁唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔識化妝又短時間練唔成既比少少錢搵人幫手化比較好<br />\n不過唔好搵伏既人化妝 望下d完成圖比較下先決定"},{"pid":"7e0f9e07f378d0425473116f68c73555593e0a37","tid":231503,"uid":92,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20120924/large/24va022p101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120924%2Flarge%2F24va022p101.jpg&h=b7ab38a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc518762ebc9ed18ca81cf8c61639b41f8575e53","tid":231503,"uid":69729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"我165 冇波得腳 皮膚白 想著啲特別d又show到自己長處既裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae0767eebea5afeb46f78557de996f8c1d397e9","tid":231503,"uid":5893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我165 冇波得腳 皮膚白 想著啲特別d又show到自己長處既裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你樓上張圖已經解答左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15544f0381ca934254a456074b7da15937adc5a","tid":231503,"uid":59314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我165 冇波得腳 皮膚白 想著啲特別d又show到自己長處既裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n著深/鮮色既可以突顯膚色<br />\n鮮色少人著 一般人難carry<br />\n深色例如黑白色好易撞<br />\n絲打有腳而且生得高<br />\n可以著長度係膝頭對上少少裙<br />\n唔會太短而且show到對腳"},{"pid":"2ad18dacc4f74cc59a7be44f31751ef576e677de","tid":231503,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"女啊?<br />\n化番個大濃妝浸啲雞味出黎扮吓大人先啦"},{"pid":"b9ef0ba702ddbf25f7d334b47bf5ba1484e6477c","tid":231503,"uid":69729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我165 冇波得腳 皮膚白 想著啲特別d又show到自己長處既裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n著深/鮮色既可以突顯膚色<br />\n鮮色少人著 一般人難carry<br />\n深色例如黑白色好易撞<br />\n絲打有腳而且生得高<br />\n可以著長度係膝頭對上少少裙<br />\n唔會太短而且show到對腳</blockquote><br />\n我frd叫我著紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7c9563b7bd9905f9ef20c59e5f3f02865ceeeb","tid":231503,"uid":9251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:48:34.000Z","msg":"Ig嘅話我覺得lazy_closet幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人買過？"},{"pid":"bb2f2f106cebf7279fd9611bcd39026089042bf9","tid":231503,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:53:18.000Z","msg":"買咩都哂氣<br />\n過兩日都係會柒到唔敢睇"},{"pid":"59428b9179678461f4d9643402c64fb5ac498d0c","tid":231503,"uid":59314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我165 冇波得腳 皮膚白 想著啲特別d又show到自己長處既裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n著深/鮮色既可以突顯膚色<br />\n鮮色少人著 一般人難carry<br />\n深色例如黑白色好易撞<br />\n絲打有腳而且生得高<br />\n可以著長度係膝頭對上少少裙<br />\n唔會太短而且show到對腳</blockquote><br />\n我frd叫我著紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你皮膚白你朋友叫你著紅都好正常<br />\n咁唔一定要鮮紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲好多唔同既紅去選擇既"},{"pid":"e94f7e2309c34cf4660b2d16d4c9416a61ccb606","tid":231503,"uid":106706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我165 冇波得腳 皮膚白 想著啲特別d又show到自己長處既裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n著深/鮮色既可以突顯膚色<br />\n鮮色少人著 一般人難carry<br />\n深色例如黑白色好易撞<br />\n絲打有腳而且生得高<br />\n可以著長度係膝頭對上少少裙<br />\n唔會太短而且show到對腳</blockquote><br />\n我反而覺得淺色裙正d 白色裙容易carry個人後生 不過你膚色如何 白就白色裙 如果黑就深色裙 白色裙都可以有不同既圖案蕾絲 都幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb30ec82d2c73506f4cf4eb251eae2095441d3d","tid":231503,"uid":106706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>紙片人表示好難買到裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知去邊度買好</blockquote><br />\n唔好著低胸<br />\n著背心cutting呢類大路款<br />\n著吊帶款都唔錯<br />\n你生得高既話著高跟鞋show下腳都已經好靚<br />\n最緊要識突顯自己既優點<br />\n我個條其實都係商場逐間行逐間睇先搵到<br />\n搵日得閒同個朋友去行個圈交換下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n斯打真係同我同路人 想法一致 最重要唔好濃妝 咪嚇死人 唔識化妝就自己練習下 淡妝都好過濃 紙片人就買d蕾絲裙好d 瘦人顯得有氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n濃妝真係大忌<br />\n我個陣有個好pure既同學化濃妝搞到好似老左5年咁<br />\n但係佢著既裙係好小妹妹feel既白色裙搞到成個look勁唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔識化妝又短時間練唔成既比少少錢搵人幫手化比較好<br />\n不過唔好搵伏既人化妝 望下d完成圖比較下先決定</blockquote><br />\n如果化妝片都可以參考下hana ram 大佬b neat freaks diary  （戴定帽 講化妝係幾好 唔評論拍片者性格）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}